title: Episode 332: Numb Ass (Feat. Queen Key & Just Pam)
itunes:title: Episode 332: Numb Ass (Feat. Queen Key & Just Pam)
description:
Rapper, Queen Key and Comedian, Just Pam join the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get wild! Have you ever had your ass ate til it went numb? Queen Key has! The ladies discuss a range of topics including: the craziest place they've had sex, sloppy vs neat head, holding back their squirt, and much more! Queen Key also gets open and honest when discussing the pain and journey of giving birth to triplets. Lastly, a major thank you to Laura Mora for guest hosting this week! Enjoy!
